                                    TEAMS
_____________________________________________________________________________________

GET /api/teams/ - Get list of all teams
POST /api/teams/ - Create a new team ----- JSON ->  {"name" : "name for team"}
GET /api/teams/{id}/ - Get information about a specific team
PUT /api/teams/{id}/ - Update information about a specific team ----- JSON ->  {"name" : "name for team"}
DELETE /api/teams/{id}/ - Delete a specific command

                                    PERSONS
_____________________________________________________________________________________

GET /api/persons/ - Get list of all persons
POST /api/persons/ - Create a new person ----- JSON ->
              {
                 "first_name" : "first_name",
                 "last_name" : "last_name",
                 "email": "email@gmail.com",
                 "team" : {pk}
              }

GET /api/persons/{id}/ - Get information about a specific person
PUT /api/persons/{id}/ - Update information about a specific person ----- JSON ->
              {
                "first_name": "first_name",
                "last_name": "last_name2",
                "email": "emaeil@gmail.com",
                "team": 1
              }

DELETE /api/persons/{id}/ - Delete a specific person


